      <title>民主党将大型石油调查送交司法部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/big-oil-investigation-sent-to-justice-department-by-democrats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会调查的结论是，指控大型石油公司数十年来在气候变化的影响方面欺骗公众，民主党人要求司法部对主要石油公司及其贸易团体进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/big-oil-investigation-sent-to-justice-department-by-democrats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰指控泽连斯基前助手非法敛财</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/ukraine-accuses-former-zelenskiy-aide-of-illicit-enrichment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰反腐败机构通知弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基办公室前副主任，他涉嫌非法致富，因为总统面临越来越大的压力，要求他展示反腐败斗争的成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/ukraine-accuses-former-zelenskiy-aide-of-illicit-enrichment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 16:17:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMLO 称 Vulcan 拒绝了对墨西哥海岸资产 20 亿美元的收购报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/amlo-says-vulcan-rejected-2-billion-bid-for-mexico-coast-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统表示，Vulcan Materials Co. 拒绝了墨西哥政府以 20 亿美元购买其加勒比海岸资产的提议，并补充说该州并未征用该资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/amlo-says-vulcan-rejected-2-billion-bid-for-mexico-coast-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 16:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
